\": \"girls\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"Geldenhuys\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am ecstatic and I feel truly blessed to run the Olympic qualifier.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic qualifier\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It takes some pressure off because now I know I have the automatic qualifying time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some pressure\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"the automatic qualifying time\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Geldenhuys admitted, however, that she needed to slice a chunk off her personal best of 54.47 if she hoped to make it through to the Olympic final inParis in August.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Geldenhuys\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"a chunk\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic final inParis\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From here it's much harder work to get the times down because if I want to make the final I need to run 53.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much harder work\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"the times\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I definitely feel it's within reach.\\\"\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reach\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's 400m hurdles final on Friday, Lindukhule Gora stunned the rest of the field to win gold in 49.45.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goparaju_Ramachandra_Rao\", \"score\": 0.9993888705892263, \"rank\": 0.000536969572284520